---
/**
 * Exploration Section - Creative Under Construction
 * 
 * DESIGN PHILOSOPHY: "The Future in Motion"
 * - Playful but technical message
 * - Suggests high-dimensional activity
 */
---

<section id="explore" class="sr-explore">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sr-explore__content">
      <div class="sr-explore__icon">🏗️</div>
      <h2 class="sr-explore__headline">Protocol Exploration Laboratory</h2>
      <div class="sr-explore__terminal">
        <div class="sr-explore__terminal-header">
          <span class="sr-explore__dot sr-explore__dot--red"></span>
          <span class="sr-explore__dot sr-explore__dot--yellow"></span>
          <span class="sr-explore__dot sr-explore__dot--green"></span>
          <span class="sr-explore__terminal-title">skillrail-discovery --mode=beta</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sr-explore__terminal-body">
          <p class="sr-explore__text">> status: <span class="sr-explore__highlight">ARCHITECTING_THE_FUTURE</span></p>
          <p class="sr-explore__text">> loading: [■■■■■■■■□□] 82%</p>
          <p class="sr-explore__text">> message: Our interactive protocol visualizer is currently being calibrated in a high-dimensional sandbox. We're optimizing the cryptographic optics to ensure total transparency.</p>
          <p class="sr-explore__text">> estimate: Ready when the blocks align perfectly.</p>
          <div class="sr-explore__cursor"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sr-explore__footer">
        While we calibrate, please refer to the <a href="#docs">technical documentation</a> to explore the protocol's mathematical foundation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sr-explore {
    padding: var(--section-padding-vertical-desktop) var(--section-padding-horizontal);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sr-explore__content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .sr-explore__icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .sr-explore__headline {
    font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .sr-explore__terminal {
    background-color: #1a1b26;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    text-align: left;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-slate-700);
  }

  .sr-explore__terminal-header {
    background-color: #24283b;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .sr-explore__dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .sr-explore__dot--red { background-color: #f7768e; }
  .sr-explore__dot--yellow { background-color: #e0af68; }
  .sr-explore__dot--green { background-color: #9ece6a; }

  .sr-explore__terminal-title {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #565f89;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .sr-explore__terminal-body {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
    color: #a9b1d6;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sr-explore__text {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .sr-explore__highlight {
    color: var(--color-indigo-light);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .sr-explore__cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px;
    height: 1.2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-indigo-light);
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .sr-explore__footer {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .sr-explore__footer a {
    color: var(--color-indigo);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    from, to { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sr-explore {
      padding: var(--section-padding-vertical-tablet) var(--section-padding-horizontal-mobile);
    }
    
    .sr-explore__headline {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .sr-explore__terminal-body {
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
    }
  }
</style>
